overview.en: Ethena is a synthetic dollar protocol built on Ethereum that will provide a crypto-native solution for money not reliant on traditional banking system infrastructure, alongside a globally accessible dollar denominated savings instrument - the 'Internet Bond'.
overview.zh: Ethena是一个基于以太坊构建的合成美元协议，它将提供一种不依赖传统银行系统基础设施的加密原生解决方案，同时还有一个全球可访问的以美元计价的储蓄工具 - '互联网债券'
